==Mandarin==

===Etymology===
Literally: Below one person, above 10,000 people.

===Pronunciation===
[[Pinyin]]: yī rén zhī xìa, wàn rén zhī shàng

===Phrase===
'''[[一]][[人]][[之]][[下]],[[万]][[人]][[之]][[上]]''' ([[Simplified Chinese]])

# (''idiom'') To occupy a lofty position, second only to the emperor.

===Alternate forms===
[[一]][[人]][[之]][[下]],[[萬]][[人]][[之]][[上]] ([[Traditional Chinese]])

